#: theme/templates/home/cookies_policy.html:24
msgid ""
"A client cookie is a text file sent to the User's <sup><a href=\"#fn1\">1</"
"a></sup> browser and stored on the hard drive of their device (e.g. PC, "
"laptop or mobile phone) when they visit a website or online platform."
msgstr ""

#: theme/templates/home/cookies_policy.html:31
msgid ""
"Client cookies can be used, for example, to ensure the proper functioning of "
"a website or platform and to optimise its usability and its functionalities."
msgstr ""
"Client cookies worden bijvoorbeeld gebruikt om de goede werking van een "
"website of platform te verzekeren en de bruikbaarheid en functies ervan te "
"optimaliseren."

#: theme/templates/home/cookies_policy.html:37
msgid ""
"SERIMA <sup><a href=\"#fn2\">2</a></sup> uses client cookies that are "
"necessary for its proper functioning, namely a cookie for managing the "
"approval of cookies (persistent cookie named \"cookiebanner\"), a cookie "
"that records the session (persistent cookie named \"sessionid\"), a cookie "
"that records the language (named \"django_language\" and stored for the "
"duration of the session) and a cookie for the CSRF token (persistent cookie "
"named \"csrftoken\")."
msgstr ""

#: theme/templates/home/cookies_policy.html:45
msgid ""
"They are stored by SERIMA in a directory provided for this purpose on the "
"User's computer or mobile device."
msgstr ""
"Ze worden door SERIMA opgeslagen in de hiertoe beschikbare map op het "
"apparaat van de Gebruiker."

#: theme/templates/home/cookies_policy.html:50
msgid ""
"Session cookies are deleted from the User's computer or mobile device when "
"their session is closed."
msgstr ""
"Sessiecookies worden verwijderd van het apparaat van de Gebruiker wanneer "
"die de sessie beëindigt."

#: theme/templates/home/cookies_policy.html:55
msgid ""
"However, unless the User takes action, persistent cookies remain on the "
"User's computer or mobile device after the end of the session for less than "
"an hour."
msgstr ""
"Permanente cookies blijven na de sessie minder dan een uur op het apparaat "
"van de Gebruiker staan, tenzij die actie onderneemt om dat te voorkomen."

#: theme/templates/home/cookies_policy.html:61
msgid ""
"The User may, at any time, choose to adjust their browser settings so that "
"cookies are not accepted and stored. Furthermore, they can delete cookies "
"that have already been stored at any time via their browser. However, the "
"use of certain SERIMA functionalities may be limited or disabled if the User "
"refuses SERIMA cookies. It is therefore recommended that the User adjusts "
"his browser settings so that SERIMA cookies are accepted."
msgstr ""
"De Gebruiker kan ook altijd in de browserinstellingen aangeven dat cookies "
"niet mogen worden aanvaard en opgeslagen. Bovendien kunnen opgeslagen "
"cookies ook gelijk wanneer via de browser worden verwijderd. Als de "
"Gebruiker SERIMA-cookies weigert, worden bepaalde functies van het platform "
"echter beperkt of uitgeschakeld. We raden Gebruikers dan ook aan om cookies "
"van SERIMA te accepteren."

#: theme/templates/home/cookies_policy.html:72
#: theme/templates/home/cookies_policy.html:75
msgid "Term defined in Article 1 of SERIMA's Terms of Use."
msgstr ""
"Begrip gedefinieerd in artikel 1 van de Gebruiksvoorwaarden van SERIMA."

