msgstr "Overdracht van rechten"

#: theme/templates/home/terms.html:666
msgid ""
"The Operator and the User may not assign all or part of their rights and "
"obligations arising from or in connection with the Terms of Use to third "
"parties or substitute a person for its performance without the written "
"agreement of the ILR."
msgstr ""
"De Operator en de Gebruiker mogen hun rechten en verplichtingen die "
"voortvloeien uit of verband houden met de Gebruiksvoorwaarden, niet geheel "
"of gedeeltelijk overdragen aan derden of een persoon vervangen voor de "
"uitvoering ervan zonder schriftelijke toestemming van het ILR."

#: theme/templates/home/terms.html:676
msgid "Miscellaneous"
msgstr "Varia"

#: theme/templates/home/terms.html:679
msgid ""
"If, by virtue of a legal provision of public order or mandatory law, one of "
"the clauses of these Terms of Use is found to be null and/or void and/or "
"unenforceable against the Operator or the User, this nullity or "
"unenforceability shall not affect the other clauses of these Terms of Use, "
