#: theme/templates/home/terms.html:688
msgid ""
"For any comments, questions or complaints relating to SERIMA, the User may "
"contact the ILR via the following e-mail address: <a href=\"mailto:"
"serima@ilr.lu\">serima@ilr.lu</a>."
msgstr ""

#: theme/templates/home/terms.html:694
